{
  "stem": "617.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And somehow they communicated that to him, but he had not-- he didn't want to hear of it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because they said, the family, we can't take the whole family, just you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he didn't want to stay behind, because he could have.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They would have had him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It didn't take long.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It take-- I don't really remember whether we slept over or it was just the one day.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I think we must have slept over.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We must have slept over in the wagons.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But somehow I don't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I know when we got there, we were very busy putting up the shelters out of sheets what we had taken.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were approximately-- four to five weeks, we were in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we already-- Shavu'ot we were celebrating in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And during that time already, or the-- after about four weeks people were starting to leave.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, they were taking them away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We never knew where.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "All we just knew that people are being transported out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To tell you the truth, I don't really remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we all thought people who leave, that's not a good sign, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were better off to stay.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we were happy that we were not the ones who are selected to leave at that time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Until it was our turn in the beginning of June, the end of May or the beginning of June.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were all put on-- into cattle cars, into trains, and we were shipped out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were about 50, 60 to a car, like the-- one of the cars.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was in Simleu that we left-- from where the ghetto was, because I think the trains were coming into that area-- there were tracks because of the brick factory there.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
